snippet.title: Mega Man Zero/ZX Legacy Collection - Announce Trailer
snippet.description:
MISSION START! Mega Man Zero/ZX Legacy Collection brings six intense action games (Mega Man Zero 1-4, Mega Man ZX & ZX Advent) to PS4, XB1, Switch, and PC on January 21!
More Info: http://bit.ly/MMZZXLC
